    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at this model risk level. The relative hemolysis index predictions satisfy the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all five operating points with a maximum relative error of 9.7%. The assessment team notes that the primary rheology and boundary-condition dataset (dataVintage 2025-10-01) predates the January 2026 model revision; updated rheological characterisation is planned for Q2 2026 to confirm continued compliance. On the basis of the current evidence package the credibility assessment is accepted.",
